        <div class="full-width-video-lede-text-below__content">
            <h1 class="full-width-video-lede-text-below__hed">This Company Is Japan’s Top Contender for Global Internet Domination</h1>
            <div class="full-width-video-lede-text-below__dek"><p>Recruit Holdings wants&nbsp;to attract the most consumers in the world by 2030.</p></div>
            <div class="full-width-video-lede-text-below__byline">
                By <div class="author">Reed Stevenson
        <div class="author__modal">
            
            
            <a class="author__modal-bio" href="https://www.bloomberg.com/authors/AQ22wJLbDiE/reed-stevenson" rel="author">More stories by Reed Stevenson</a>
        </div>
    </div>
                <div class="full-width-video-lede-text-below__times">
                    
